the ant, the heart of the ant?

240
00:16:51,648 --> 00:16:55,637
It does have a heart and it beats.

241
00:16:55,637 --> 00:16:57,764
It's not like our heart but it does have
a

242
00:16:57,764 --> 00:16:58,264
heart.

243
00:16:58,264 --> 00:17:00,300
It has a circulatory system

244
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:09,779
and God controls that as if it is the only
creature in the universe.

245
00:17:09,779 --> 00:17:12,993
So, when God says, in SURAH 53

246
00:17:12,993 --> 00:17:15,861
"God is the One who makes you happy
or miserable.

247
00:17:15,861 --> 00:17:18,430
God is the One who makes you rich or poor."

248
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:26,298
And when we raise the new understanding, which
is absolutely essential for you to go to Heaven,

249
00:17:26,298 --> 00:17:28,785
namely,
God is doing everything.

250
00:17:30,494 --> 00:17:34,899
We need to know who God is to understand
and appreciate that statement.

251
00:17:34,899 --> 00:17:37,297
God is doing everything.

252
00:17:38,403 --> 00:17:42,619
The only thing we do is choose to be with
God or with Satan.

253
00:17:42,619 --> 00:17:43,384
This is it.

254
00:17:43,987 --> 00:17:46,762
After that God takes over.

255
00:17:46,762 --> 00:17:50,885
And God makes you rich or poor, happier or
miserable.

256
00:17:50,885 --> 00:17:53,270
God is doing everything.

257
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:56,240
However, misery comes from Satan.

258
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:59,440
But in accordance with God's will.

259
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:01,962
So, the Ultimate Doer is God.

260
00:18:01,962 --> 00:18:07,120
And we bring the misery on themselves... on
ourselves.

261
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:10,008
We choose to put our finger in the fire or
not.

262
00:18:10,008 --> 00:18:14,236
So, when it hurts, it's because we chose to
put our finger in the fire.

263
00:18:14,236 --> 00:18:18,793
And it is God's law that when you put your
finger in the fire, it hurts.

264
00:18:18,793 --> 00:18:20,611
So, we bring the pain on
ourselves.

265
00:18:22,755 --> 00:18:29,153
So, if you have any problem of any kind, you
just have to ask yourself

266
00:18:29,153 --> 00:18:30,995
"why do I have this problem?"

267
00:18:30,995 --> 00:18:34,678
And you have to dig and find out why and remove
the

268
00:18:34,678 --> 00:18:35,410
reasons.

269
00:18:35,410 --> 00:18:37,318
You have to be honest with yourself.

270
00:18:41,572 --> 00:18:42,715
AQEM AL-SALAT.

271
00:18:43,084 --> 00:18:47,167
ALLAH-O AKBAR, ALLAH-O AKBAR, LA ILAHA ILLA ALLAH.

272
00:19:01,874 --> 00:19:03,613
الله اکبر

273
00:19:05,452 --> 00:19:07,340
(1:1) بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ

274
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:10,198
(1:2) ٱلْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ

275
00:19:10,198 --> 00:19:11,913
(1:3) ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ

276
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:13,974
(1:4) مَـٰلِكِ يَوْمِ ٱلدِّينِ

277
00:19:13,974 --> 00:19:16,828
(1:5) إِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَإِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِينُ

278
00:19:16,828 --> 00:19:19,246
(1:6) ٱهْدِنَا ٱلصِّرَٰطَ ٱلْمُسْتَقِيمَ

279
00:19:19,246 --> 00:19:25,971
(1:7) صِرَٰطَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ غَيْرِ ٱلْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا ٱلضَّآلِّينَ

280
00:19:25,971 --> 00:19:28,356
الله اکبر

281
00:19:32,876 --> 00:19:34,740
سمع الله لمن حمده

282
00:19:35,846 --> 00:19:37,846
الله اکبر

283
00:19:43,824 --> 00:19:45,495
الله اکبر

284
00:19:46,601 --> 00:19:47,629
الله اکبر


